Comment: 50,0:23:52.99,0:23:53.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 50,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.00,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Shota, look, it's her!{end of ep2 vv}
Dialogue: 50,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.34,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,The girl on the stage!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.38,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This way, Lilly! {end of ep2 ^^}
Dialogue: 50,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.43,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,Lilly-san!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.93,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.56,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:38.52,0:00:39.52,Default,Crowd A,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lilly-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:39.52,0:00:40.56,Default,Crowd B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shake my hand!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.02,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Excuse us! Make way please!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.52,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Lilly!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's Sho-chan and his friend!{sho-chan-tachi implies she knows kadoya too, but his name doesn't come up organically before this}
Dialogue: 50,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.49,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Is it true you just debuted today?!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:50.49,0:00:52.49,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of yours!
Dialogue: 50,0:00:53.37,0:00:53.99,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 50,0:00:55.41,0:00:57.04,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 50,0:00:57.04,0:00:58.75,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Your performance was awesome.
Dialogue: 50,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.17,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.17,Default,Crowd A,0,0,0,,Lilly-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.88,Default,Crowd B,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.42,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What now? There's no escape!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:11.93,0:01:13.05,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.39,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula,
Dialogue: 50,0:01:16.39,0:01:18.52,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,make us fly away from this!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:23.69,0:01:24.65,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 50,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.40,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 50,0:01:25.90,0:01:28.57,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I cast a spell, but...
Dialogue: 50,0:01:30.74,0:01:33.66,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Excuse us! {\i1}Please{\i0} make way!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.05,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I messed up again!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.76,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,You stink. You're not wishing hard enough.
Dialogue: 50,0:01:51.76,0:01:53.64,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.26,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.81,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:59.81,0:02:00.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.25,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,That was amazing...
Dialogue: 50,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.25,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 50,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.60,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I should continue my homework.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.52,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We made it.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.28,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This is my agency!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.40,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.58,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Your agency is in {\i1}here?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.04,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't what I pictured at all!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:42.93,0:04:43.93,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:48.10,0:04:48.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.85,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Take a seat.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.19,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.77,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.16,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Wait right there. I'll put on some tea.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.91,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.75,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.17,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.63,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.88,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the girl you talked about?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:18.26,0:05:21.30,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yep! She's our next big talent!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.43,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Ah, he's our agency's president.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.64,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.77,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,I keep telling you,\Nyou're way too impulsive.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.56,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But I just found our future star!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.61,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I can't just sit on this and relax.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.19,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You saw her concert too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.74,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Even if I did...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:42.45,0:05:48.33,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm Toko's uncle,\Nand the agency's president,
Dialogue: 50,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.04,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,Kandachi Yasuo.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.54,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It's too much of a hassle\Nto do everything myself,
Dialogue: 50,0:05:55.54,0:06:00.13,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,so I founded the agency\Nand made my uncle the president.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.43,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,You just started going off about\Nwanting to be an idol.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.97,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,It was a pretty big burden, y'know.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:05.97,0:06:10.22,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Really? You were lazing about so much,\NI figured you had time to kill.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:12.56,0:06:17.65,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We're still pretty small,\Nbut we're on track to get even bigger!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.65,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,And now we have just the member\Nto help us with that!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.49,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.91,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Come on, Toko-san!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.16,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We can pull through with you on our side!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.54,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm still not cut out for this!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.00,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.54,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, Toko's found you, so you must be for real.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.25,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.12,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,So, Lilly-chan?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.42,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Wanna join the agency and work with us?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:40.21,0:06:40.92,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.30,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Didn't you enjoy being up on stage?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.30,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I know you can shine even brighter than that!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.47,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.60,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.73,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I said we'd have some yummy food.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Don't want you getting hounded again,
Dialogue: 50,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.23,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,so how does takeout from the café next door sound?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.48,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yummy food?!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.65,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Their pasta is super good!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.24,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We can get parfaits too!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.99,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.74,Default,Yasuo,0,0,0,,You think that'll win her over?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.50,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello, this is Once More!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.62,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}Can I place an order\Nfor two servings of pasta and parfaits?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.54,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Man, I'm starving.\NWhen's it gonna get here?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.51,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.51,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Sena. How'd it go?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.47,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Did you find the studio?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:29.10,0:07:29.76,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.39,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,They'd said they liked me.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.14,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:35.14,0:07:39.36,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,So many girls explode with popularity\Nafter modeling for that magazine!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.73,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It's basically the entryway to idolhood!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.78,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.07,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,They might even ask you\Nto be their exclusive model!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.49,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,You're getting ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.08,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.91,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This is Aozono Sena, a member of the agency.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.87,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,She's my classmate in high school.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.38,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.26,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This is our new member, Lilly-san.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:04.26,0:08:07.05,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I-I haven't decided if I wanted to join yet!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.31,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Yeah, Toko's a hard one to shake.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.56,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Glad to work with you, Lilly.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's, um, my pleasure.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.40,Default,Delivery,0,0,0,,Delivery from Café Love-Love!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.90,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.07,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.96,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Kabappy?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, do you like Kabappy?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.26,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Sort of, yes.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.51,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You do? Me too!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.85,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Neat.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.14,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Alright, you two!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.77,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.69,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It looks so good!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.10,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Where's my food?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.56,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Sorry, didn't get you any.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.40,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Can we split your pasta, then?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.07,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That was the plan.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.07,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I know how much you like this.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.16,Default,Sena,0,0,0,,Some parfait too.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.58,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.01,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Being in an agency is actually...
Dialogue: 50,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,kind of fun.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:33.84,0:09:38.47,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It's not just fun and games.\NWe're serious about this.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:39.02,0:09:39.68,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.85,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I want to give it a try.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.11,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You do?!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.44,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.11,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Let's do this together!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:50.07,0:09:53.70,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So what do I have to do as an idol?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.92,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.17,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Fuu.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.80,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Phew, I had a blast!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.05,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Really? What were you up to?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.47,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hmm... well, you see...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.93,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Did something good happen to her?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.90,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Dinner will be ready soon!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.57,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:31.19,0:10:36.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Uguisu, today sure was full of fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.33,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.79,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I had so much fun.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I got to perform out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 50,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.42,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,and ended up joining an agency.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.34,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I forgot Kabappy at the agency!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.21,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Klutz.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Whatever. Time to sleep.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.72,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.53,Default,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\i1}Su-Sugar Sugarly La Lu Sugarin'
Dialogue: 50,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.03,Default,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll coat even your sighs in sugar
Dialogue: 50,0:11:15.03,0:11:18.49,Default,CompatoLilly,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the same old bustling intersection
Dialogue: 50,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.21,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,So Lilly...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.96,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,really did just debut today.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.47,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,And she still gave such\Nan amazing performance...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.22,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.73,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all seemed like a fairy tale on the screen
Dialogue: 50,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.86,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something far, far away...
Dialogue: 50,0:11:57.28,0:12:01.70,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I used to love singing, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:03.45,0:12:08.29,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made a wish to the stars
Dialogue: 50,0:12:08.29,0:12:12.75,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Up in the twinkling sky
Dialogue: 50,0:12:13.21,0:12:18.05,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}The clouds in the sky are so fluffy{revised for context of next line which wasn't in ep1}
Dialogue: 50,0:12:18.05,0:12:22.51,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like cotton candy
Dialogue: 50,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.02,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You're so good, big sis!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:25.56,0:12:27.18,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Can you sing more?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.52,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.73,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Fuu, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.15,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,But one day, just as\NI was about to head to school...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:45.12,0:12:45.91,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Rui?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.25,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NAre you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.17,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.92,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'm... okay...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.92,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Good...bye.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Rui?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:59.63,0:13:00.55,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Rui?!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:04.97,0:13:09.89,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I fell sick and went\Nto the hospital for a long time.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.02,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I couldn't even go to school.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.11,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.78,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 50,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.74,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,All the time I spent alone\Nafter I got sick
Dialogue: 50,0:13:27.16,0:13:30.58,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,became a part of me\Nsomewhere along the way.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.13,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey, big sis!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.51,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 50,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.35,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 50,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.74,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I think I forgot how to sing too.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:02.53,0:14:08.12,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,But Lilly's song made my heart throb.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:08.79,0:14:12.62,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,It's as if those emotions\NI've forgotten are coming back.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.29,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.01,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Want to give it a try, then?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.39,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.31,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Darn, I overslept.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Morning, big sis.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.02,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Good morning, Fuu.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.12,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,B-Big sis?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.46,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.00,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's a real mountain.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.84,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Looks delicious to me!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.09,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I had no idea Rui liked anko paste that much.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.39,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, she {\i1}was{\i0} raised in a confectionery shop.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.22,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Did you see it yesterday?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.60,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.44,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.27,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,I watched it over and over again!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.98,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What'cha talking about?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.99,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,There was this amazing show\Nin Shibuya yesterday!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.15,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,By this girl named CompatoLilly!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.99,Default,Classmate,0,0,0,,Her performance was super cool!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.58,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,She's this mystery idol, right?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.79,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Yeah! Her livestream was super big\Nand went viral!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.33,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,She was just so cute!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.42,Default,Classmate,0,0,0,,I want to be just like her!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not all that...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.55,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Uhh, I haven't heard about that!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:47.09,0:15:50.30,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,You haven't? Are you living under a rock?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.56,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's almost time for class!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.56,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,They still haven't revealed anything about Lilly.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.07,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,I guess that's how they're marketing her.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.32,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,No one knows her real name or age either.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:05.32,0:16:10.07,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Oh... Now I'm even more invested in her!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.58,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,Her singing is so good,\Nand she's so cute.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.87,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,I could listen to her forever.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.33,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.31,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.40,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.90,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Let's try...
Dialogue: 50,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.41,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:50.99,0:16:55.66,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Shota, since our club is off next week,\Nwanna go out somewhere?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.21,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Right before the end-of-term exam? No way.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.54,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, man.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.96,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Are you studying at all, Kadoya?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.09,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.17,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Well, you should.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.68,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Anyways, I'm so curious\Nabout that girl from yesterday.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.51,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,That I agree with.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:13.64,0:17:14.93,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Nonoyama?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.68,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,What on earth is she doing?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.81,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.19,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Hey, Nonoyama!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.82,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 50,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.11,Default,Hisashi,0,0,0,,Off she goes.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.28,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,What's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.16,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I read up a bit at the library.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.83,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,A lot about magic is still\Nbeyond our understanding.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.59,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:44.96,0:17:45.71,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:46.21,0:17:50.80,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,But I figured I'd prepare some\Nbefore I start casting magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Big sis!{end of ep1 vv}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.35,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I took in these cats!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.10,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.35,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,They're very cute.{end of ep 1 ^^}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.98,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Azuki, I'm Rui. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.82,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,So your name is Rui!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.95,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,What a cute name.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.83,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I am not an ordinary cat.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.83,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I come from a magical land.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:23.67,0:18:27.21,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Y-You're... talking...?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:27.92,0:18:32.17,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Everything I say must stay a secret\Nbetween us, okay?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.09,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Even from your family.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.26,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Rui, you can use magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:41.43,0:18:45.85,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,If you have strong feelings,\Nyou can use magic.{to qcer: i think i got a wording rev on this line in ep1, for now i'm staying for consistency but may alter in both eps for batch}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.36,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I could tell from the moment\NI met you before.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.78,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for startling you.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:55.32,0:18:59.87,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I believe you will cast wonderful spells.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.00,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,So would you like to give it a try?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.58,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 50,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.88,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.09,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.96,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Then I'll go back to being a cat.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.85,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I wonder if we have any black curtains at home.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.89,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,As for the offering...\Nshould I go with some confectioneries?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.02,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Offering?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:24.52,0:19:25.98,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,It was in the book I read.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.06,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,They say preparation is key for casting magic,
Dialogue: 50,0:19:29.06,0:19:32.53,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,so, since it's my first time,\NI want to make sure I get it right.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.03,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:36.95,0:19:37.86,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Let's get back!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.79,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.82,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.40,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is what you meant by preparing?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.57,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah. I read up about it.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.16,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I think she has the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 50,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.07,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,I'll leave it be.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.41,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.83,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Let's begin, Azuki!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.33,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.50,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I've been thinking it over since then.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.34,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I think I really do want to sing.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.10,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Do you remember the words I taught you?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.06,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:55.15,0:20:55.98,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Letto.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.38,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Lululila pululila!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.05,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Pop'n pam!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.22,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,You're beautiful!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:18.69,0:22:19.69,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 50,0:22:20.28,0:22:21.53,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,me?
