Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.48,0:22:54.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I feel so lonely{淋しそうに}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(I was always right beside you){『当たり前に隣に居た』}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I'm searching for you{君を探してる}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I'll frame a photo of us two and hang it up{二人映る 額縁(frame)Decorate！}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.45,0:23:06.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Let's set things the way we want, the way we will, the way they are{思うがまま ワガまま ありのままに並べよう}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.78,0:23:10.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Take our chemistry, plus+, minus-, multiplied×, divided÷ by...{相性 Plus＋ Minus－ Multiply× Divide÷ by…}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.20,0:23:10.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I love it every way{「全部好き」}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.95,0:23:14.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Calling me, calling you{Calling me Calling you}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(And you){「＆you」}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}I want to walk up the stairs of the future with you{君と歩きたい 未来階段(stairs)}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Lucky lucky shiny, our beating hearts dreamin' away{Lucky Lucky Shiny 二人の ときめきDreamin’}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.80,0:23:24.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}If there's clear skies tomorrow, everything will be okay{明日晴れなら 万事オーライ}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.97,0:23:28.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Maybe I'm a bit sad and weak{ちょっとブルー Weakness}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.43,0:23:29.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(But I'm happy!){(but happy)}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.43,0:23:32.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}But when I'm with you I feel safe{けど君が居るから Being saved}
